  <brief_title>High Frequency Stimulation of the GPi or Thalamus in Tourette's Syndrome</brief_title>
  <official_title>Pilot Study of Internal Globus Pallidus or Median Centre of the Thalamus High Frequency Stimulation for the Treatment of Patients With Severe Tourette's Syndrome</official_title>
